<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Bryan </PERSON> <PERSON> Brumley </PERSON>, a former <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> correspondent in <LOCATION> Warsaw </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Moscow </LOCATION>, writes on national security affairs from <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>.
