<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 Here is the text of the statement by <ORGANIZATION> White </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> press secretary <PERSON> Marlin </PERSON> <PERSON> Fitzwater </PERSON> announced early Wednesday that President <PERSON> Bush </PERSON> had ordered American troops in <LOCATION> Panama </LOCATION> to seize dictator <PERSON> Manuel </PERSON> <PERSON> Antonio </PERSON> <PERSON> Noriega </PERSON>.
