We thought it was an attractive window to access the public equity markets,'' he said. `` However, the window did not appear as attractive as it might have been.'' <PERSON> Grant </PERSON> said the company has not ruled out issuing the stock at a later time. TLC <PERSON> Beatrice </PERSON> owns 15 companies, including <ORGANIZATION> Franprix </ORGANIZATION>, a food wholesaler in the <LOCATION> Paris </LOCATION> area; <LOCATION> Tayto </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Ireland </LOCATION>'s largest snack food company; and seven ice cream distributors in <LOCATION> Europe </LOCATION>.
